{"type":null,"faqId":38974,"title":"智能闹钟如何使用？","answer":"<p>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"></p>\n\"您好，智能闹钟功能可以设置一个提前提醒时间，如果您在闹钟响铃时间之前的一段时间内，处于浅度睡眠状态，手环会提前叫醒您。如果您处于深度睡眠状态，手环不会打扰您，会在正常的闹钟时间将您叫醒。<br>\n请保持手环和手机蓝牙连接正常，设置时间后，点击界面右上角 √ 完成闹钟设置，并将闹钟设置信息同步到手环。<br>\n说明：<br>\nAndroid用户请根据APP界面提示同步数据，iOS用户请回到APP主界面下拉同步数据，同步成功后闹钟设置才可以生效。<br>\n如果您设置闹钟的时候，手环和手机蓝牙连接不正常，您的设置信息会在下次手环和手机蓝牙连接正常，重新打开APP同步数据的时候生效。\"\n<br>\n<br>\n<p></p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4284","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":34,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}